HOTEL RESERVATION SYSTEM - SERVER

README

1. INTRODUCTION
	This is the server part of the hotel reservation system.

2. INSTALLATION

	a.	Install virtualenv if not installed
		by using sudo apt-get install virtualenv

	b.	mkdir server

	c.	cd server

	d.	virtualenv flask

	e.	flask/bin/pip install flask

	f.	Place all the files in the 'server' folder

	g.	Change any settings in app.py if needed

3. RUNNING THE SERVER

	a. Run the script app.py from the terminal



